window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Most all the magical races are under attack from a secret threat.</b></p> <p>Gnomes, giants, elves, and fairies are dying worldwide. <i>Is it magicians or mortals behind the attacks?</i></p> <p>Gen Beaufont is charged with discovering the truth since she already has a lead on the case. The person behind this is suspected to be the true evil that will push Gen into her ultimate role. This will be her finest hour as she unveils her first real nemesis and the biggest threat to magic.</p> <p><i>Who will step out of the shadows?</i></p> <p>This is the battle that will change everything.</p> <p><i>Can Gen Beaufont save the magical races before they are eliminated for good?</i></p> <p>Or will this new evil wipe out all who stand in their way?</p>"; 
